{"type": "article", "id": 30399, "title": "食物造型的线香座", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-01T23:05:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160801173822OktsE8FwRhu0gq36.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>谁说线香座不可以变得有趣好玩儿？由澳大利亚一对设计师好友创立的品牌 NONCENSE 最近就以食物作为灵感设计了三款线香座，这些栩栩如生的香蕉、披萨和煎蛋均由手工打造而成。每款线香座都随印有品牌 logo 的木盒寄送，还附赠一个黑色的托特包。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.noncense.com.au/products\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 150 澳元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801181202jlqIxi9c04wHNB7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608011811359KmOlHT4fuIdY3DC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801181135rkvlQEYPxBWm2z5O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608011811351KSqIBegYMQDRPVH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}